Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Medicine, inventions and the quick-fix
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjgbg
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 8 May 1998
The desire for a 'quick-fix', the false dawns of the daily medical miracle, the instant imitation of new inventions and excitement over a 'so-called' impotence pill.